title: Pinetop Perkins - Live At Antone's Vol. 1 (2015) [FLAC]
description:
Classic blues reissue from Pinetop Perkins with some other members of the Muddy Waters Blues Band and special guest Kim Wilson ( The Fabulous Thunderbirds). This remastered album features 4 previously unreleased bonus tracks from the original live recording session at Antone's nightclub, Austin, TX in July 1995, for Antone's 20th anniversary. 


Pinetop Perkins - Live At Antone's Vol. 1
Label: New West Records
Format: WEB, 14 files FLAC, Album, Reissue, Remastered, Expanded, 16bit 44.1kHz
Released: 2015
Originally released 2000
Recorded in July 1995 at Antone's Nightclub, Austin, Texas
Genre: Blues
Style: Chicago Blues
